query:
SELECT w.id, w.status, w.reportFilename, COUNT(s.id) as stakeholder_count 
FROM workflows w 
LEFT JOIN stakeholders s ON w.id = s.workflowId 
WHERE w.id = (SELECT MAX(id) FROM workflows)
GROUP BY w.id
